snippet: State Sen. Ron Calderon pleaded not guilty Monday to federal charges that he accepted $100,000 in bribes in return for pushing legislation, charges that could send him to federal prison for years....

headline.print_headline: California Senator Pleads Not Guilty to Corruption
headline.main: California Senator Pleads Not Guilty to Corruption

lead_paragraph: State Sen. Ron Calderon pleaded not guilty Monday to federal charges that he accepted $100,000 in bribes in return for pushing legislation, charges that could send him to federal prison for years.
